"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The irony here is that many of these institutional investors who are passively holding PoS tokens originally began investing in the digital asset space to hedge against inflation on real-world assets, and they are now experiencing even higher rates of inflation on their PoS tokens.\\n\\n[According](https://staked.us/yields/) to Staked, the average rate of supply inflation for the top 25 PoS tokens is around 8%, which is far above real-world numbers. Meanwhile, token stakers earn yields above the inflation rate, as rewards are made up not only of newly created tokens but also transaction fees. On average, stakers earn 6.4% per year in real yield. The contrast is clear: Passive holders suffer 8.2% inflation on their investment, potentially paying another 1.8%â€“2.3% in management fees if invested via an ETP, while stakers earn 6.4% in real yields.\",\"timestamp\":1639034410,\"title\":\"The irony here is that many of these institutional investors\"},\"digest\":\"znNawsPo7YepuaWwjD5N55gmmSD1RKlvtMDBaVW9U7U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xBA0c67c116CF20B42ED60932D804518900e1A9d7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cSAIEJGLXSPhL0IZcJ3E983vjWbaZeA05BjmXMNdQHc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Zjr0hLkxhvI4aTswOmT5mbPlH8Lw4OUK3tK8Xkwo7QQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"S43Y6CL3Nwp7_0_yoWPz9nXPZQZauA4U0ecY8Tu2PYE0PVQ6HwZIUiKfKFQv-KUgNWAB9eIGrsgCiDLo6C9xMA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5bf8d633d065e008773b5d892c84700b0ab8ecc6b7d98bcd13be311f2ae8e5d86afe5732f5eafae72b135be08918fcf62942d4df976c27bfda0baf8de9974a081c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cSAIEJGLXSPhL0IZcJ3E983vjWbaZeA05BjmXMNdQHc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Zjr0hLkxhvI4aTswOmT5mbPlH8Lw4OUK3tK8Xkwo7QQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-25